latestPosts.caption:
Not every trend is worth the hype, it’s just new name to same old thing, known as “Drag proof makeup”. Being in the market we too have to use such names just to attract clients …
But as I said any good makeup with good technique is long lasting and drag proof only 

Treat makeup as makeup not cement that you want this proof that proof, water proof, sweat proof, I mean common who throws water on your face on your big day, who pours coke on your face, who rubs your face 🙃 much needed common sense nothing else 

So don’t ask your mentors to teach you specially drag proof makeup as it’s already there, if you are going for a good mentor they will give you a right direction and will let you know reality check too 

Same good old thing with new names, pls just don’t get confused… if I would have just written, no one would believe it so making proper video on it will surely do its things .
People don’t believe on words but the proofs !!!

Makeup & hairstylist: @priyachoithani_dsolitaire @d_solitaire_makeovers
